headline: 4 Integrated Energy Stocks to Gain Despite Industry Weaknesses
summary: Softer crude prices, slowing production growth and mounting renewable demand are making the prospects for the Zacks Oil & Gas US Integrated industry gloomy. ConocoPhillips (COP), Occidental (OXY), National Fuel (NFG) and Epsilon (EPSN) are well placed to survive the challenges.
